buri.ddmsence.ddms.summary.xlink

Class XLinkAttributes

  • Object
    • buri.ddmsence.AbstractAttributeGroup
      • buri.ddmsence.ddms.summary.xlink.XLinkAttributes

  • public final class XLinkAttributes
extends AbstractAttributeGroup
    Attribute group for the XLINK attributes.

    In DDMS2.03.03.14.0.1/4.15.0

    This class only models the subset of attributes and values that are employed by the DDMS specification. Determinations about whether an attribute is optional or required depend on the decorated class (Link, RevisionRecall, or TaskID).
